


 MamaPutOnline (Nwaanyi Akwa Foods)

Root Thought (Project Goal)

> You are a Senior UI/UX Designer and Senior Frontend Engineer specializing in modern food delivery websites.

> Your objective is to build a premium Nigerian food delivery landing page using only **HTML5 and Tailwind CSS** (no JavaScript and no inline CSS).

> The website should look like a professional product that could compete with Uber Eats, Chowdeck, Glovo, and DoorDash while maintaining a strong Nigerian identity.

> Design should be mobile-first, highly responsive, reusable, accessible, and visually appealing.



