Tailwind Best Practices



Use

* reusable utility classes
* max-width containers
* flex
* grid
* gap utilities
* responsive breakpoints
* transitions
* hover effects
* rounded corners
* shadow hierarchy

Avoid

* inline CSS
* duplicate classes
* unnecessary wrappers


